This is the place for all things BaseElements plugin.

All the documentation is here :

(https://github.com/GoyaPtyLtd/BaseElements-Plugin/tree/master/docs)

We do not provide free technical support or implementation help with the plugin, but feel free to ask questions on the Discussions page :

(https://github.com/GoyaPtyLtd/BaseElements-Plugin/discussions) 

Or post something to Issues : (https://github.com/GoyaPtyLtd/BaseElements-Plugin/issues) if you have a bug or problem with building the plugin.

If you're having a plugin related issue with one of our products such as the BaseElements developer tool, there is a specific product related support site for BaseElements : (https://docs.baseelements.com).

